             was indicted for <rs id="t18230910-310-off1661" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18230910-310-off1661" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18230910-310-off1661" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18230910-310-cd1662" type="crimeDate">17th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18230910-310-off1661 t18230910-310-cd1662"></join>, a watch, value 30 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18230910-310-victim2667" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Rigby
                        <interp inst="t18230910-310-victim2667" type="surname" value="Rigby"></interp>
